00:01:08.909 --> 00:01:11.109
It's a story that exemplifies
the many ways in which

00:01:11.109 --> 00:01:13.685
this campus is linked to
the history of California

00:01:13.685 --> 00:01:16.159
and to the Bay Area.

00:01:16.159 --> 00:01:18.576
Dr. Charles Hitchcock, a
physician for the Army,

00:01:18.576 --> 00:01:21.444
